      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">32.110</ph> Payment of subcontractors
under cost-reimbursement prime contracts.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">If the contractor makes financing payments to a subcontractor
under a cost-reimbursement prime contract, the contracting officer
should accept the financing payments as reimbursable costs of the
prime contract only under the following conditions:</p>
         <ol id="d2026e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2051e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The
payments are made under the criteria in <xref href="Subpart_32.5.dita#FAR_Subpart_32_5"
                        base="i1082047"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  32.5</xref> for
customary progress payments based on costs, <xref href="32.202-1.dita#FAR_32_202_1"
                        base="i1083117"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.202-1</xref> for commercial product or commercial service purchase
financing, or <xref href="32.1003.dita#FAR_32_1003"
                        base="i1080969"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.1003</xref> for performance-based
payments, as applicable.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2051e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> If customary
progress payments are made, the payments do not exceed the progress
payment rate in <xref href="32.501-1.dita#FAR_32_501_1"
                        base="i1082067"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.501-1</xref>,
unless unusual progress payments to the subcontractor have been
approved in accordance with <xref href="32.501-2.dita#FAR_32_501_2"
                        base="i1082080"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.501-2</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2051e37">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> If customary
progress payments are made, the subcontractor complies with the
liquidation principles of <xref href="32.503-8.dita#FAR_32_503_8"
                        base="i1082368"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.503-8</xref>, <xref href="32.503-9.dita#FAR_32_503_9"
                        base="i1082371"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.503-9</xref>, and <xref href="32.503-10.dita#FAR_32_503_10"
                        base="i1082397"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.503-10</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2051e51">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> If performance-based
payments are made, the subcontractor complies with the liquidation
principles of <xref href="32.1004.dita#FAR_32_1004"
                        base="i1080976"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.1004</xref>(d).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2051e59">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph> The subcontract
contains financing payments terms as prescribed in this part.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
